chunk_content: Use a deployed fine-tuned modelAfter your fine-tuned model deploys, you can use it like any other deployed model. You can use the Playground in Azure AI Studio to experiment with your new deployment. You can also use the REST API to call your fine-tuned model from your own application. You can even begin to use this new fine-tuned model in your prompt flow to build your generative AI application.> [!NOTE]> For chat models, the system message that you use to guide your fine-tuned model (whether it's deployed or available for testing in the playground) must be the same as the system message you used for training. If you use a different system message, the model might not perform as expected.
